title: Bright 3 level townhome
map_address: 3085 Old Highway 8 near County Road D
app_fee: $35.00 (Credit, criminal, income and rental history verifications)
posting_body: ['I have a very nice, updated 2 bedroom townhome on 3 levels in the Roseville/New Brighton area available for a October move in time frame.', 'It rents for $1,425.00 and the deposit is the same.', 'This unit features a fully finished basement with a walk in storage closet and separate laundry room.', 'The basement is carpeted with nice, bright lighting and is cable ready with plenty of electric outlets.', 'The main level has an updated kitchen with tons of cupboard space and newer appliances.', 'There is a half bath on this level as well.', 'Off of the kitchen, there is a large deck (10x16) with steps onto the common lawn.', 'The living room is large with big windows and the entry has a closet.', 'On the top level you have your full bath with huge linen closet and both bedrooms.', 'The larger bedroom is about 13x12 and the smaller is about 10x10.', 'Both have big closets with mirrored doors.', 'Each bedroom has a ceiling fan and bright big newer windows with window treatments.', 'The townhome comes with a single car garage and there is an outdoor pool that is open from Memorial Day to Labor Day.', 'There is a well maintained central air and gas forced air furnace.', 'These townhomes are very centrally located near ample shopping and close to both downtowns.', 'Come on out and take a look.', 'You won’t be disappointed.', 'It is in a very quiet area with convenient access to 35W.', 'We have a very reliable maintenance team and 24 hour call answering for our townhomes.', 'You will never need to worry about your home being in disrepair.', 'Deposit is one months’ rent and we do not accept dogs.', "If you'd like to arrange a showing to see the availability, please e-mail, text or call Bryan at", 'show contact info', '.', 'Please reference Roseville townhomes.']
